        "rules": [
          {
            "rule_number": "11.1",
            "summary": "1. (1) The PRA directs that, with effect from 27 May 2014, Part XXII of FSMA (Auditors and Actuaries) applies to the carrying on of insurance business by members as modified by (2).",
